plot_for_loop <- function(df, x_var, y_var) {
  
  ggplot(df, aes(x = .data[[x_var]], y = .data[[y_var]])) + 
    geom_point() + 
    geom_line() +
    labs(x = x_var, y = y_var) +
    theme_classic(base_size = 12)
}
